---
title: PackML lifecycle + Alarm sub-state
---
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> INIT
    INIT --> BOOTING: power
    BOOTING --> STARTING: kernel ready
    STARTING --> LOADING_TAGS: rings online
    LOADING_TAGS --> IDLE: tags hydrated
    LOADING_TAGS --> OFFLINE: load fail

    IDLE --> EXECUTE: start cmd
    EXECUTE --> RUNNING: tick
    RUNNING --> COMPLETE: done
    RUNNING --> HOLDING: hold cmd
    HOLDING --> HELD: settled
    HELD --> UNHOLDING: resume
    UNHOLDING --> RUNNING: resumed

    RUNNING --> STOPPING: stop cmd
    STOPPING --> STOPPED: settled
    STOPPED --> CLEARING: reset
    CLEARING --> IDLE: cleaned

    RUNNING --> ABORTING: abort
    HELD --> ABORTING: abort
    ABORTING --> ABORTED: settled
    ABORTED --> CLEARING: reset

    COMPLETE --> BLOOMED: ok
    BLOOMED --> IDLE: cycle

    state Alarm {
        [*] --> NONE
        NONE --> ACTIVE: PV crosses threshold
        ACTIVE --> ACKED: operator ack
        ACKED --> CLEARED: PV in band
        ACTIVE --> CLEARED: self clear
        CLEARED --> NONE: reset
    }

    RUNNING --> Alarm: any tag breach
    HELD --> Alarm: any tag breach
    Alarm --> RUNNING: cleared
